Class OmniWheelDrive.SpecificParams

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.SCHSRobotics.HAL9001.system.robot.subsystems.OmniWheelDrive.SpecificParams
  • Enclosing class:
    OmniWheelDrive 

    public static final class OmniWheelDrive.SpecificParams
extends Object
    A class used for entering necessary params while in config mode or for using more specific versions of params than can be set with the config.
